# ADK Synapser

Skill: `.cursor/skills/livskompassen-synapser-adk/SKILL.md`  
Connections: `.cursor/skills/livskompassen-synapse-connections/SKILL.md`  
Runtime: `functions/src/adk/synapses/synapseBus.ts`, `stateStore.ts`

## Triggers

| Trigger | Handler | Status | Effekt |
|---------|---------|--------|--------|
| `drive_file_ingested` | `driveIngestSynapse` | **live G10** | Drive → klassificering → `reality_vault` / `kb_docs` / `children_logs` / `inbox_queue` — **MUST NOT** bevis → `kb_docs` |
| `journal_woven` | `journalWovenSynapse` | **done G7** | Opt-in → `kampspar`; idempotent per `journalEntryId` |
| `dcap_alert` | `dcapAlertSynapse` | **live** | DCAP risk ≥70 / ALERT → WORM `dcap_alerts` (hashed input) |
| `user_overwhelm` | `paralysBrytarenSynapse` | **live** | Ett mikrosteg via bus (`breakDownResponse`) |

